About us
Dongguan Sunun Power CO.,LTD, its predecessor, Shenzhen Sunun Power Technology CO.,LTD, which was founded in 2008, locates in Humen town,Dongguan, China. We have been focusing on the developing, manufacturing and selling of power supply products such as as AC adaptors,battery chargers,USB wall chargers,open frame power supplies,PD adapters,car chargers,USB data cables,etc.We have more than 10 years of professional power supply factory experienceare and we are dedelicated to becoming the world's leading professional provider of intelligent & efficient power products and Solutions. Currently, we have two plants,one is in Dongguan,the other new plant is in Shaoguan Guangdong.We have 8 finished production lines (Dongguan + Shaoguan) with daily output of more than 150,000sets of power supply products.Our company has passed IS09001:2008 quality system certification,ISO14001:2008 quality system certification, ISO14001 environmental management system and OHSAS18001 (Occupational Health and Safety Management System)certification. Our power supply products have been passed UL,GS,PSE,KC,BIS,BSMI,TISI,3C,CQC,CB,FCC and ROHS certifcations. Our power products sells well not only in China Mainland, but also in other countries and regions like USA,Europe,Japan,Korea,and south-east Asia, etc. Many well-known customers at home and abroad, like Amazon, AT&T, Hama, SUNNY, CHANGHONG,OGAWA,TINECO, etc, all have chosen us therir partners for long-term coopeartion.
